how to display bluetooth battery (wireless headset) on linux mint (if in DE Gnome, kde plasma, and xfce it doesn't seem necessary)
1. open the terminal
2. type sudo nano /etc/bluetooth/main.conf
3. in the [General] section add Experimental = true
4. when you have, press the ctrl + x key to exit and save.
5. and press enter
6. after that, we just restart the bluetooth services, namely systemctl restart bluetooth
7. done
